580
01:21:02,191 --> 01:21:04,103
Granddad.

581
01:21:05,277 --> 01:21:07,314
Granddad.

582
01:21:10,491 --> 01:21:13,199
I think I'm dying, Granddad.

583
01:21:15,954 --> 01:21:17,991
Aren't we all?

584
01:23:40,682 --> 01:23:42,674
Be seeing you, Birdie.

585
01:23:44,228 --> 01:23:45,890
Toss?

586
